messages.messageBody:
Sorry. Yahoo--or my 'puter---has the hiccoughs again!

Yes, August 19th. My birthday! <g> 43. The Early Bird Deadline is over, but
regular registration is until August 19th. You can still register at the door,
but then the price is per person.

Thanks, Barb!
~Kelly
